              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontsize='12'>• Customer churn rate is 26.58%</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontsize='12'>• Logistic Regression achieved 78.04% accuracy</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontsize='12'>• 65 customers were identified as high risk</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontsize='12'>• High-risk customers represent approximately $69K annual revenue</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontsize='12'>• Month-to-month contracts exhibit the highest churn propensity</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontsize='12'>• Retention efforts should prioritize high-risk segments</run>
